WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:28.480 --> 00:00:37.400
Thus song was written in memory of one of my former students, who passed away at a young age

00:00:37.400 --> 00:00:45.400
She was a sweet and cheerful person. In the music, I aimed for a lighter tone and mood so as to reflect her personality. A funereal dirge wouldn't have suited her.

00:00:45.400 --> 00:00:46.760
Rest in Peace,  Kitty

